title: Possibily Our Last Episode - Frenemies #3
description: On this episode of Frenemies Trisha explains that Ethan annoyed her enough that she is thinking about quitting. Also we talk about her music video shoot, Anthony Padilla, Gabbie Hanna, Ethan's milkers, and a whole lot more!
